496
00:29:18,924 --> 00:29:20,217
Apa?

497
00:29:21,218 --> 00:29:22,261
Begini...

498
00:29:22,761 --> 00:29:25,097
Itu akan menyenangkan.

499
00:29:25,180 --> 00:29:28,892
Akan segera kupindahkan Jeong Hyeok
ke Pyongyang.

500
00:29:30,352 --> 00:29:32,938
Kami akan carikan apartemen di sana,

501
00:29:33,522 --> 00:29:35,607
dan membeli perabot.

502
00:29:35,691 --> 00:29:37,067
Kau tak perlu menyiapkan.

503
00:29:37,150 --> 00:29:39,069
Astaga. Tapi

504
00:29:39,987 --> 00:29:41,530
kami tak bisa lakukan itu.

505
00:29:41,613 --> 00:29:43,782
Kami harus beli perabot dan perkakas.

506
00:29:44,366 --> 00:29:45,659
Perabot dan perkakas?

507
00:29:45,742 --> 00:29:50,247
Nyonya, kau tampaknya
tak menyadari tren terkini.

508
00:29:50,330 --> 00:29:53,375
Perabotan itu kabinet, laci kasur,
kloset, rak buku, dan rak sepatu.

509
00:29:53,458 --> 00:29:55,919
Perkakasnya kulkas, mesin cuci,

510
00:29:56,003 --> 00:29:57,963
